data.description: Home Sweet Home! Convenience and comfort in Mableton! Large Fenced Backyard with Screened Deck for entertaining. Three Bedrooms upstairs including the Owner's Suite with Tray Ceiling and Walk-In Closet. Owner's Bath with Double Vanity and Separate Tub & Shower. Laundry Room Upstairs - WASHER & DRYER INCLUDED! Guest Room with Full Bath on the Main Level. Eat-In Kitchen with Custom Cabinetry, Granite Counters, and Stainless Appliances. REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED! Amazing Two-Story Great Room with Fireplace and Wall of Windows for lots of light. Formal Dining room and Living Room or Office. Full almost Finished Terrace Level with High Ceilings, Media Room, Full Bath, and Bedroom. Extra Parking Pads for guests along with the 2 car garage. Electric Car Charger Included! - 240 Volt Level 2 Charger. Call Agent today for easy showing!
